<subSubSection id="24CB1080FF90FFCEFAB2AA5B84D3FA3B" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="6C6E430BFF90FFCEFAB2AA5B84D3FA3B" blockId="36.[151,1437,793,1504]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">
<emphasis id="5EA59F19FF90FFCEFAB2AA5B815EFAAB" bold="true" box="[199,315,1333,1359]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">Remarks.</emphasis>
Previous records from the coast of São Paulo include Ilhabela (Ilha de São Sebastião), Peruíbe, and Cananéia (
<collectingCountry id="14C6039BFF90FFCEFB36AA378115FA97" box="[323,368,1369,1395]" name="Iceland" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">Ilha</collectingCountry>
do Cardoso) (
<bibRefCitation id="08403EFAFF90FFCEF86DAA37837DFA97" author="Rocha, S. S. &amp; Bueno, S. L. S." box="[536,792,1369,1396]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" pagination="1001 - 1010" refId="ref75515" refString="Rocha, S. S. &amp; Bueno, S. L. S. (2004) Crustaceos decapodes de agua doce com ocorrencia no Vale do Ribeira de Iguape e rios costeiros adjacentes, Sao Paulo, Brasil. Revista Brasileira de Zoologia, 21 (4), 1001 - 1010. https: // doi. org / 10.1590 / S 0101 - 81752004000400038" type="journal article" year="2004">Rocha &amp; Bueno 2004</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="08403EFAFF90FFCEF950AA378439FA97" author="Pileggi, L. G. &amp; Mantelatto, F. L." box="[805,1116,1369,1395]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" pagination="194 - 208" refId="ref73529" refString="Pileggi, L. G. &amp; Mantelatto, F. L. (2010) Molecular phylogeny of the freshwater prawn genus Macrobrachium (Decapoda, Palaemonidae), with emphasis on the relationships among selected American species. Invertebrate Systematics, 24 (1), 194 - 208. https: // doi. org / 10.1071 / IS 09043" type="journal article" year="2010">Pileggi &amp; Mantelatto 2010</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="08403EFAFF90FFCEFE1CAA378539FA90" author="Mossolin, E. C. &amp; Pileggi, L. G. &amp; Mantelatto, F. L." box="[1129,1372,1369,1396]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" pagination="605 - 613" refId="ref71160" refString="Mossolin, E. C., Pileggi, L. G. &amp; Mantelatto, F. L. (2016) Crustacea, Decapoda, Palaemonidae, Macrobrachium Bate, 1868, Sao Sebastiao Island, state of Sao Paulo, southeastern Brazil. Check List, 6 (4), 605 - 613. https: // doi. org / 10.15560 / 6.4.605" type="journal article" year="2016">
Mossolin 
<emphasis id="5EA59F19FF90FFCEFEAEAA34856AFA97" box="[1243,1295,1369,1395]" italics="true" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">et al</emphasis>
. 2016
</bibRefCitation>
). The occurrence in 
<collectingRegion id="AE158DE9FF90FFCEFB40AA138244FA7C" box="[309,545,1405,1432]" country="Brazil" name="Rio Grande do Norte" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">Rio Grande do Norte</collectingRegion>
and 
<collectingRegion id="AE158DE9FF90FFCEF822AA138286FA73" box="[599,739,1405,1431]" country="Brazil" name="Pernambuco" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">Pernambuco</collectingRegion>
states (northeastern 
<collectingCountry id="14C6039BFF90FFCEF9BCAA13846AFA7C" box="[969,1039,1405,1432]" name="Brazil" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">Brazil</collectingCountry>
) is doubtful since it was mentioned in compilation studies without documented records (see 
<bibRefCitation id="08403EFAFF90FFCEF973AACF83AAFA5F" author="Pileggi, L. G. &amp; Magalhaes, C. &amp; Bond-Buckup, G. &amp; Mantelatto, F. L." box="[774,975,1441,1468]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" pagination="563 - 574" refId="ref73652" refString="Pileggi, L. G., Magalhaes, C., Bond-Buckup, G. &amp; Mantelatto, F. L. (2013) New records and extension of the known distribution of some freshwater shrimps in Brazil. Revista Mexicana de Biodiversidad, 84, 563 - 574. https: // doi. org / 10.7550 / rmb. 30504" type="journal article" year="2013">
Pileggi 
<emphasis id="5EA59F19FF90FFCEF92EAACC83EEFA5F" box="[859,907,1441,1467]" italics="true" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">et al</emphasis>
. 2013
</bibRefCitation>
for details). Sequences accession number (GenBank): CCDB 2137—16S (
<accessionNumber id="7382DEE8FF90FFCEF871AAAB82EEFA04" box="[516,651,1477,1504]" httpUri="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/nucleotide/HM352454" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">HM352454</accessionNumber>
), COI (
<accessionNumber id="7382DEE8FF90FFCEF8A8AAAB8304FA04" box="[733,865,1477,1504]" httpUri="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/nucleotide/HM352494" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">HM352494</accessionNumber>
) (
<bibRefCitation id="08403EFAFF90FFCEF90DAAAB84CFFA3B" author="Pileggi, L. G. &amp; Mantelatto, F. L." box="[888,1194,1477,1503]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" pagination="194 - 208" refId="ref73529" refString="Pileggi, L. G. &amp; Mantelatto, F. L. (2010) Molecular phylogeny of the freshwater prawn genus Macrobrachium (Decapoda, Palaemonidae), with emphasis on the relationships among selected American species. Invertebrate Systematics, 24 (1), 194 - 208. https: // doi. org / 10.1071 / IS 09043" type="journal article" year="2010">Pileggi &amp; Mantelatto 2010</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
